text: Posts: 54,486 The Latest: Bautista gets Jays within 2-1 of Royals in ALCS (Yahoo Sports) The Blue Jays won Game 5 to force the series back to Kansas City, where the Royals still lead 3-2. The Mets await the winner in the World Series after sweeping the Cubs. Game 6 of the AL Championship Series is underway.
